N1  - E62. The study's findings suggest that GenAI-powered TA has the potential to address barriers related to effective feedback mechanisms and adaptive learning content customization.. 
N1  - E63. To achieve this, TA-related barriers should be addressed through adequate prompt engineering, incorporating established taxonomies of questions and effective tutoring strategies.. 
