N1  - E67. Students should have sufficient learning sessions to learn, discuss, and assimilate subject-matter knowledge and skills before interacting with TAs.. 
N1  - E68. Furthermore, students' prior knowledge and attitudes towards the subject matter should be examined to identify the needs and support individual students require.. 
